        "subject": "LU-3496 ost: convert devlock from spinlock into rwlock",
        "message": "LU-3496 ost: convert devlock from spinlock into rwlock\n\nThis patch converts devlock into rwlock so as to reduce\nlock contention for dev_{set,check}_rdonly functions.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Perepechko <andrew_perepechko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Boyko <Alexander_Boyko@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: alexander_zarochentsev@xyratex.com\nReviewed-by: Vitaly Fertman <Vitaly_Fertman@xyratex.com>\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-999\nChange-Id: I9984bdf65eb079b46901b4ccec0a49ad8867e439\n"
